Add CUDA kernel analyzer, memory manager, and TPU distillation optimizers
- Implemented KernelAnalyzer for profiling and analyzing CUDA kernel performance, including metrics for occupancy, memory usage, and execution time. - Developed CUDAMemoryManager for efficient memory allocation and management on CUDA, featuring a memory pool and defragmentation capabilities. - Introduced versioning and compatibility checks for CUDA environment. - Created TPU-optimized distillation kernels and layer optimizers, enhancing knowledge transfer between teacher and student models. - Added adaptive mechanisms for layer-wise optimization, including dropout rates and attention patterns. - Implemented efficient layer normalization and feed-forward network optimizations tailored for TPU execution.
